OL,5, The billionaire founder of the outdoor 
OL,6, fashion retailer Patagonia says he has 
OL,7, given away his company to a charitable 
OL,8, trust.                                 
OL,10,FYvon Chouinard said that under a new   
OL,11,Fownership structure, any profit not    
OL,12,Freinvested in running the business     
OL,13,Fwould go to fighting climate change.   
OL,15,FThis will amount to around $100bn      
OL,16,F($86bn) a year, he claimed, depending  
OL,17,Fon the health of the company.          
OL,19,FPatagonia sells hiking and other       
OL,20,Foutdoor clothing in over 10 countries. 
